        # Basic charts
        
        ![Line Chart](https://github.com/freyastreamlit/streamlit-lightweight-charts/blob/main/examples/LineChart.png?raw=true)
        
        ```python
        import streamlit as st
        from streamlit_lightweight_charts import renderLightweightChart
        
        chartOptions = {
            "layout": {
                "textColor": 'black',
                "background": {
                    "type": 'solid',
                    "color": 'white'
                }
            }
        }
        
        seriesLineChart = [{
            "type": 'Line',
            "data": [
                { "time": '2018-12-22', "value": 32.51 },
                { "time": '2018-12-23', "value": 31.11 },
                { "time": '2018-12-24', "value": 27.02 },
                { "time": '2018-12-25', "value": 27.32 },
                { "time": '2018-12-26', "value": 25.17 },
                { "time": '2018-12-27', "value": 28.89 },
                { "time": '2018-12-28', "value": 25.46 },
                { "time": '2018-12-29', "value": 23.92 },
                { "time": '2018-12-30', "value": 22.68 },
                { "time": '2018-12-31', "value": 22.67 },
            ],
            "options": {}
        }]
        
        st.subheader("Line Chart sample")
        renderLightweightChart( chartOptions, seriesLineChart, 'line')
        ```
